"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncomputedshapesourcedatasource","type":"topic","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Data source for ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource","type":"reference"},{"text":". This protocol defines two optional methods for fetching","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"data, one based on tile coordinates, and one based on a bounding box. Classes that implement this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"protocol must implement one, and only one of the methods. Methods on this protocol will not be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"called on main thread, they will be called on the caller’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"requestQueue"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNComputedShapeSource":{"abstract":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":" is a map content source that supplies vector shapes,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"one tile at a time, to be shown on the map on demand. You implement a class"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conforming to the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol that returns"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instances of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"type":"text","text":", then add a computed shape source to an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"i